---
title: Coat 'n' Roast Chicken Dinner with Smashed Potatoes and Broccoli
description: This super simple chicken just requires a quick mix and toss, then you're off to the races! Our creamy smashed potatoes and roasted broccoli round out this meal perfectly!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-enrobe-roti-719649fb.jpg
